        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "∴相似比为$\\frac{A D}{B C}=\\frac{8}{10}=\\frac{4}{5}=\\frac{M A}{M B}=\\frac{M D}{M C}$ $\\frac{A D}{B C}=\\frac{8}{10}=\\frac{4}{5}=\\frac{M A}{M B}=\\frac{M D}{M C}$ ",
          "block_bbox": [
            207,
            2053,
            2164,
            2270
          ],
          "block_id": 6,
          "block_order": 4
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "\n$\\frac{\\Delta M A D 周钛 }{\\Delta M B C 周長 }=\\frac{4}{5}\\textcircled{1}$ ",
          "block_bbox": [
            139,
            2280,
            1375,
            2541
          ],
          "block_id": 7,
          "block_order": 5
        },
        {
          "block_label": "formula",
          "block_content": "\\frac{M A}{M B}=\\frac{4}{5}\\therefore\\frac{M A}{M A+4}=\\frac{4}{5}\\therefore M A=16 O ",
          "block_bbox": [
            345,
            2559,
            2096,
            2770
          ],
          "block_id": 8,
          "block_order": 6
        },
        {
          "block_label": "formula",
          "block_content": "O \\frac{M D}{M C}=\\frac{4}{5}\\therefore\\frac{M D}{M D+5}=\\frac{4}{5}\\therefore M D=20",
          "block_bbox": [
            325,
            2804,
            2104,
            3044
          ],
          "block_id": 9,
          "block_order": 7
        },
        {
          "block_label": "text",
          "block_content": "\n$\\Delta M A D 四边 =M A+A D+M D=16+8+20$ ∴由①②可矢O.△MBC周长=55",
          "block_bbox": [
            134,
            3304,
            1622,
            3460
          ],
          "block_id": 10,
          "block_order": 8
        },
        {
          "block_label": "formula",
          "block_content": "∴由①②可矢O.△MBC周长=55\\Delta M A D 四边 =M A+A D+M D=16+8+20 O ",
          "block_bbox": [
            310,
            3065,
            2149,
            3313
          ],
          "block_id": 11,
          "block_order": 9
        }
      ],
      "markdown": "看到\n\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"imgs/img_in_image_box_638_124_1973_1318.jpg\" alt=\"Image\" width=\"53%\" /></div>\n\n\n再看到周去\n\n相化比=周长比\n\n'$A D//B C$ $\\Delta M A D\\sim\\Delta M B C$ ]\n\n∴相似比为$\\frac{A D}{B C}=\\frac{8}{10}=\\frac{4}{5}=\\frac{M A}{M B}=\\frac{M D}{M C}$ $\\frac{A D}{B C}=\\frac{8}{10}=\\frac{4}{5}=\\frac{M A}{M B}=\\frac{M D}{M C}$ \n\n\n\n$\\frac{\\Delta M A D 周钛 }{\\Delta M B C 周長 }=\\frac{4}{5}\\textcircled{1}$ \n\n$$\\frac{M A}{M B}=\\frac{4}{5}\\therefore\\frac{M A}{M A+4}=\\frac{4}{5}\\therefore M A=16 O $$\n\n$$O \\frac{M D}{M C}=\\frac{4}{5}\\therefore\\frac{M D}{M D+5}=\\frac{4}{5}\\therefore M D=20$$\n\n\n\n$\\Delta M A D 四边 =M A+A D+M D=16+8+20$ ∴由①②可矢O.△MBC周长=55\n\n$$∴由①②可矢O.△MBC周长=55\\Delta M A D 四边 =M A+A D+M D=16+8+20 O $$",
